summary: Provides a Flax (JAX) implementation of a stable diffusion pipeline specialized for image inpainting. It preprocesses input images and masks, runs the diffusion model with configurable schedulers and optional safety checking, and outputs the inpainted results.
business_intent: Allow developers and content creators to incorporate advanced, controllable image inpainting capabilities into applications, facilitating creative editing, restoration, and generation of visuals while maintaining safety standards.
